    <section class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Limitations and Future Work</p>
      <h2>What we would do differently</h2>
      <div class="limits-grid">
        <div class="limit-card">
          <h4>Small dataset</h4>
          <p>131 samples is insufficient for deep learning. Data augmentation could substantially help.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="limit-card">
          <h4>No cross-validation</h4>
          <p>A single 70/15/15 split means results are sensitive to which samples land in each set.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="limit-card">
          <h4>Binary only</h4>
          <p>Healthy vs. Alzheimer is a simplification. Multi-class staging would be more clinically useful.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="limit-card">
          <h4>No linguistic features</h4>
          <p>Only acoustic features are used. Adding vocabulary diversity and pause patterns could improve results.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

